	* src/ggv-prefs-ui.c (ggv_prefs_dialog_new): set spacing between
	buttons.

2002-09-13  Jaka Mocnik  <jaka@gnu.org>

	* bonobo/main.c: per-display registration of factory.
	* src/main.c (create_window): graciously handle cases when no
	windows could be opened because of errors.
	* src/ggv-prefs-ui.c (ggv_prefs_dialog_new): added colons as
	suggested by Muktha.
