	* src/gtkgs.c (start_interpreter): chdir() to the current dir of
	ps file in the child process to prevent screwing up the ggv's cwd.
	* ggv/ggv.schemas: fix a typo.
	* released 1.1.93 tarball.

2001-11-18  Jaka Mocnik  <jaka@gnu.org>

